    <item>
      <title>特斯拉业绩令人失望，谷歌股价下跌 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/bloomberg-technology-07-24-2024-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 全面报道了特斯拉第二季度的业绩，因为马斯克将特斯拉的未来寄托在了延迟的自动驾驶出租车上。此外，谷歌投资者仍在等待人工智能带来回报，而 CrowdStrike 则对全球 IT 中断进行了更新。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/bloomberg-technology-07-24-2024-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国法院禁止通过电话费补贴穷人服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/phone-fee-to-subsidize-services-for-us-poor-blocked-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院表示，美国政府几十年来所依赖的为贫困和农村用户补贴电信服务的资金机制违反宪法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/phone-fee-to-subsidize-services-for-us-poor-blocked-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:50:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软《魔兽世界》游戏员工投票决定成立工会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/world-of-warcraft-unionizes-growing-foothold-at-microsoft-s-activision-blizzard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《魔兽世界》的员工投票决定将这款热门视频游戏系列成立工会，这将使微软公司的工会立足点扩大约 500 名员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/world-of-warcraft-unionizes-growing-foothold-at-microsoft-s-activision-blizzard</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据中心电力需求推动 NextEra 进入旺季</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/data-center-power-demand-pushes-nextera-to-record-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于数据中心的需求持续飙升，NextEra Energy Inc. 在第二季度增加了 3,000 兆瓦（大约相当于三个核反应堆的容量）新的可再生能源和储能项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/data-center-power-demand-pushes-nextera-to-record-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 18:10:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
